  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients suffering from high trans-sphincteric anal fistula

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Acute sepsis.

          -  Specific cause of fistula e.g. Crohn's disease

          -  Strictured anorectum.

          -  Any degree of incontinence

          -  Recurrent anal fistula.

          -  Low anal fistula.

          -  Previous anorectal surgery.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
